      <title>前信贷瑞士风险负责人华纳因莫桑比克传奇而罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/ex-credit-suisse-risk-head-warner-fined-over-mozambique-saga</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士信贷前首席风险和合规官拉拉·华纳（Lara Warner）因未能履行与莫桑比克金枪鱼钓鱼机队融资绑架的票房报告义务而被瑞士当局罚款100,000名瑞士法郎（114,000美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/ex-credit-suisse-risk-head-warner-fined-over-mozambique-saga</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 10:27:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
